      "full_name": "Skywalker Technology Co. Ltd",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Skywalker Technology Co. Ltd is a Chinese entity producing model aircraft. It has been one of the producers and developers of the “Gerbera” unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV), a mimic of the Shahed-36 UAV and ultimately produced in the Alabuga Special Economic Zone. The Alabuga Special Economic Zone hosts manufacturing facilities producing UAVs used by the Russian military in Ukraine. The “Gerbera” UAV has been used by the Russian military in Ukraine, in particular as a decoy UAV to overwhelm Ukrainian defence systems.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}